'''CrystalDiskMark'''是一個[[开放源代码|开放源代码]]的磁碟[[基準化分析法|基準測試]]工具，在Microsoft Windows上執行。以微軟的MIT授權{{link-en|DiskSpd|DiskSpd}}工具為基礎<ref name=site>{{cite web |title=CrystalDiskMark |url=https://crystalmark.info/en/software/crystaldiskmark/ |website=Crystal Dew World [en] |accessdate=2019-04-06 |quote=CrystalDiskMark 4-6 uses Microsoft DiskSpd (The MIT License). |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406035329/https://crystalmark.info/en/software/crystaldiskmark/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此圖形化基準測試工具常用於[[固态硬盘|固态硬盘]]的效能<ref>{{cite web |title=Adata XPG SX8200 Pro NVMe SSD review: Top-tier performance for a song |url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/3323075/adata-xpg-sx8200-pro-nvme-ssd-review.html |website=PCWorld |accessdate=2019-04-06 |language=en |date=2018-12-14 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406035328/https://www.pcworld.com/article/3323075/adata-xpg-sx8200-pro-nvme-ssd-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Microsoft Surface Go with 64GB eMMC storage – How much slower is the $399 model? |url=https://www.windowscentral.com/surface-go-64gb-emmc-speed-test |website=Windows Central |accessdate=2019-04-06 |language=en |date=2018-08-02 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406040413/https://www.windowscentral.com/surface-go-64gb-emmc-speed-test |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其透過與磁碟區相關的方式在[[文件系统|文件系统]]中讀寫來運作。以許多不同數量的[[異步I/O|佇列]]與[[线程|线程]]來生成循序與隨機讀寫的速度<ref>{{cite web |title=Main Window |url=https://crystalmark.info/en/software/crystaldiskmark/crystaldiskmark-main-window/ |website=Crystal Dew World [en] |accessdate=2019-04-06 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406035327/https://crystalmark.info/en/software/crystaldiskmark/crystaldiskmark-main-window/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。固態硬碟往往在隨機讀寫方面表現優異，不像[[硬盘|硬盘]]，固態硬碟不需要尋找讀寫的特定位置<ref name="HP_SSD">{{cite web |url=http://h41112.www4.hp.com/promo/blades-community/eur/en/library/weekly_comment/081027_HP-SSD-part2-v2_clean.pdf |title=Understanding Solid State Drives (part two – performance) |publisher=[[惠普|惠普]] |date=2008-10-27 |accessdate=2011-07-06}}</ref>。

有一個名為'''AmorphousDiskMark'''的[[macOS|macOS]]分支，其以固體的[[无定形体|无定形体]]命名<ref>{{cite web |title=AmorphousDiskMark for macOS - measures storage read/write performance |url=http://www.katsurashareware.com/pgs/adm.html |website=katsurashareware |accessdate=2019-04-06 |archive-date=2019-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417084543/http://katsurashareware.com/pgs/adm.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== CrystalDiskInfo ==
'''CrystalDiskInfo'''是一套用於讀取及監控磁碟狀態的MIT授權[[S.M.A.R.T.|S.M.A.R.T.]]實用工具。如同CrystalDiskMark，此工具主要用於固態硬碟，除了一般的[[高技術配置|PATA]]與[[SATA|SATA]]以外，也支援[[NVM_Express|NVMe]]連線方式。其他功能還包含了英特爾的RAID支援、電子郵件與音效警告，以及AAM/APM調整<ref>{{cite web |title=CrystalDiskInfo |url=https://crystalmark.info/en/software/crystaldiskinfo/ |website=Crystal Dew World |accessdate=2019-04-06 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406035329/https://crystalmark.info/en/software/crystaldiskinfo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 吉祥物 ==
CrystalDiskMark的開發者網站''Crystal Dew World''以著名的[[日本动画|動畫]]吉祥物水晶雫（{{lang-ja|水晶雫}}）為特色。在2012年3月的更新透過CrystalDiskMark 3.0.2的特別主題來介紹她<ref>[http://crystaldew.info/2012/10/26/crystaldiskmark-3-0-2/ CrystalDiskMark 3.0.2 Shizuku Edition] {{Wayback|url=http://crystaldew.info/2012/10/26/crystaldiskmark-3-0-2/ |date=20191102134917 }} Crystal Dew Blog</ref>。從CrystalDiskInfo 7開始，她在特別版中以日語獻聲<ref>{{cite web |title=CrystalDiskInfo 7 Shizuku Edition |url=https://suishoshizuku.com/en/software/ |website=suishoshizuku |accessdate=2019-04-06 |quote=She can speak Japanese only. |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406040920/https://suishoshizuku.com/en/software/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

